{"root":{"data":{"id":"dbf60a0u2s00","created":1752840240617,"text":"工具"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf60d0blfs0","created":1752840247117,"text":"终端","layout_right_offset":{"x":44,"y":-18},"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbf620m2nko0","created":1752840376862,"text":"开发工具","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf62vt8nug0","created":1752840444776,"text":"Mingw-w64","layout":null,"note":"**Mingw-w64是一个头文件、导入库、库和工具的集合**，与编译器工具链（如GCC或LLVM）结合使用时，可以为构建本机Windows应用程序和库提供完整的开发环境。Mingw-w64是原始mingw.org项目的进一步发展，该项目创建的目的是为了支持Windows系统上的GCC编译器。它于2007年分叉，以提供64位支持和更新的API。此后，它获得了广泛的应用和分发。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbf62you5r40","created":1752840451040,"text":"cygwin","layout":null,"note":"### 是什么\n\n\n### 核心原理\n"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbf633to5yo0","created":1752840462216,"text":"msys","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}